| -: | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | --------------------------------------- | --------------------------------- |
|  1 | `livepeek https://api.github.com/users/torvalds`                                                         | Shows GitHub profile for Linus Torvalds | Profile lookup, GitHub metadata   |
