### Tips for Usage

| Tip                        | Example                                                                                           |
| -------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| üîÑ Auto-refresh every 10s  | `livepeek https://api.coingecko.com/api/v3/simple/price?ids=bitcoin&vs_currencies=usd --watch 10` |
| üîê Custom auth header      | `livepeek https://httpbin.org/headers --header "Authorization: Bearer xyz"`                       |
| üìÇ Collapsible nested data | `livepeek https://api.spacexdata.com/v4/launches/latest`                                          |
| üß™ Try search/filter APIs  | `livepeek https://hn.algolia.com/api/v1/search?query=AI`                                          |
